POST http://localhost:8080/api/location/update?userId=1002&latitude=39.9088&longitude=116.3976

### 查询附近用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/location/nearby?userId=1001&latitude=39.9087&longitude=116.3975&radius=0.1

### 获取用户1001位置
GET http://localhost:8080/api/location/user/1001